{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"02626bcf-da20-4712-a01d-fce2bf109793","content":"Here's what to change:\n\n**1. Replace NuGet packages:**\n\nRemove:\n- `NUnit3TestAdapter`\n- `Microsoft.NET.Test.Sdk`\n\nAdd:\n- `NUnit.Runner` (≥ 4.3.0) — this is the Microsoft.Testing.Platform runner for NUnit\n\n**2. Update your `.csproj`:**\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <!-- Enable the new testing platform -->\n  <TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>\n  <!-- Required for executable entry point -->\n  <OutputType>Exe</OutputType>\n  <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>\n</PropertyGroup>\n\n<ItemGroup>\n  <PackageReference Include=\"NUnit\" Version=\"4.x\" />\n  <PackageReference Include=\"NUnit.Runner\" Version=\"4.3.0\" />\n</ItemGroup>\n```\n\n**3. Run tests with:**\n\n```bash\ndotnet test           # still works via --testingplatform-dotnet-test bridge\ndotnet run            # runs directly as an executable\n```\n\n**Key differences:**\n- Your test project becomes an executable (needs `OutputType=Exe`)\n- `NUnit.Runner` provides the entry point and platform integration\n- You can pass `--help` to the built executable to see new CLI options","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"b988143c-80c3-4167-8069-e9745f745e0a","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is asking about migrating their NUnit test project from VSTest to Microsoft.Testing.Platform. This is a knowledge question about .NET testing infrastructure migration. Let me provide a concise answer based on my knowledge.\n\nKey changes needed to migrate NUnit from VSTest (NUnit3TestAdapter) to Microsoft.Testing.Platform:\n\n1. Replace `NUnit3TestAdapter` with `NUnit.Runner` (the Microsoft.Testing.Platform runner for NUnit)\n2. Update the project file to enable the new platform\n3. Remove `Microsoft.NET.Test.Sdk` (replaced by the new runner)\n\nLet me provide a concise answer.","outputTokens":486,"requestId":"BC4D:165EF2:1C5C63F:1F6A1E6:69FA8FFA"},"id":"6c42352f-5bda-4391-805d-a8442dbafb7e","timestamp":"2026-05-06T00:49:09.077Z","parentId":"a77bcefc-9204-485f-8434-f80af7f77ac5"}
